            "text": "<p>Battle Creek Motorcycle Club has been providing premier motocross and offroad racing experiences since 1968. Our facility features multiple tracks including a main motocross track, a vintage track, and extensive offroad trails.</p><p>We host regular race events, practice days, and special competitions throughout the season. Whether you're a seasoned racer or just getting started, BCMC offers something for every skill level.</p>"
